{"tid":1175883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日男吞246包可卡因運毒 墨西哥飛東京期間抽搐暴斃","createTime":"2019-05-29T00:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T05:00:45.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"156aae23e05129cc4a1dea15ac4c1ad4996adea4","tid":1175883,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Btrmc5Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtrmc5Z.png&h=3b18883c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kECktEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkECktEk.png&h=994a8181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n一名日本男子在哥倫比亞首都波哥大飛往日本東京途中暴斃，他搭乘的班機在墨西哥北部緊急降落，當局在他體內發現246包可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥索諾拉州（Sonora）檢察署表示，42歲死者由波哥大飛到墨西哥市，再轉機飛往日本，但他轉機由墨西哥市飛往東京期間，在航程不久開始抽搐，空中服務員發現後，隨即請求緊急降落索諾拉州艾莫西約（Hermosillo）。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，飛機在24日清晨2時25分降落，醫護人員登機後宣佈男子不治。聲明未透露男子姓名，僅以有津（Udo N）稱呼他。驗屍發現這名男子吞下246包、每包長2.5厘米闊1厘米的可卡因，死因是藥物過量引發腦水腫。以人體運毒是販毒集團常用的走私手法。<br />\n<br />\n涉事班機由墨西哥國際航空公司（Aeromexico）營運，當時機上還載有198名乘客，男子遺體移下機後，飛機繼續航程。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司／中央社"},{"pid":"60ef66e30197a78f32d44019056f6614b05fb5f4","tid":1175883,"uid":178187,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qq6ph0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qq6ph0.gif&h=7e1ac778&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa74c2ed8cc86051ff054c71bd63992bf68707a9","tid":1175883,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YB0YpPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYB0YpPM.jpg&h=206b6292&s={SIZE}\" /> 唔通變左神又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}